# Live YouTube subscriber count on the footer badge.
# Google Cloud console -> enable "YouTube Data API v3" -> create an API key.
# Free at this volume: one channels.list call per hour costs 1 of 10,000 daily units.
# Server-side only. Without this, the badge degrades to a plain Subscribe link.
YOUTUBE_API_KEY=

# Contact form delivery, via Web3Forms. Dashboard -> the form -> Form Access Key.
# Public by design and shipped in the client bundle; Web3Forms treats it as a form id.
# Without this, the form renders disabled rather than dropping enquiries.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
